word_mean_info__list.difference: 指因过失而受到降级、阶格；也多指因自身的境遇而感到耻辱。
常可和degrade换用，强调降级所带来的耻辱；也多指自卑和感到渺小无能的心理状态。
指降低某人在他人心目中的地位，使其丢脸。
指损伤或剥夺自尊感，损坏自尊心，强调蒙受耻辱。
指精神和行为上的谦逊。褒义指对自己或自己的成就不骄傲；贬义指过低地评价自己，对人低声下气。
含义广泛，指行为或态度等方面不自大、不虚荣、不傲慢、不武断和不自负。

word_group.brief_definition: 内脏馅饼；低声下气；谦卑

bilingual.source: She gave a humble speech after receiving the award.
bilingual.target: 她在领奖后发表了一篇谦逊的演讲。

bilingual.source: Despite his success, he remains self-deprecating and humble.
bilingual.target: 尽管他很成功，他依然保持自嘲的和谦逊的态度。

bilingual.source: A humble attitude can help you gain more respect from others.
bilingual.target: 谦逊的态度可以帮助你获得更多的尊重。

bilingual.source: Thus, a humble partner might be your ideal partner.
bilingual.target: 因此，一个谦逊的伴侣可能是你的理想伴侣。

bilingual.source: She's a very humble athlete. It's nice to see.
bilingual.target: 她是个谦逊的运动员。很高兴见到这样的运动员。

bilingual.source: Always practise with a sincere and humble spirit.
bilingual.target: 练习时永远保持一份友善及谦逊的态度.

bilingual.source: Still, the actor finds ways to keep himself humble.
bilingual.target: 这位演员还是找到了让自己保持谦逊的方法。

bilingual.source: The humble sands couldn't move with you now, you see.
bilingual.target: 你瞧，那谦逊的沙子都不能与你移游向前了。

bilingual.source: Leaning Tower of Pisa humble, ancient Sicily, Positano and distracted.
bilingual.target: 谦逊的比萨斜塔、古朴的波西塔诺和意乱情迷的西西里。

bilingual.source: He, like his teammates, is very humble, and prefers to defer to Duncan.
bilingual.target: 和他谦逊的队友们一样，他也表示邓肯才是更合适的人选。

list.abstract:
英 ['hʌmbl] 美 ['hʌmbl]
Humble Me 轻视我 ; 谦逊的我 ; 虚心的我 ; 客气的我
humble pie 内脏馅饼 ; 道歉 ; 低级馅饼 ; 屈辱
humble a谦虚的 ; 谦逊的 ; 地位低下的
Defeat and failure make people humble. 挫折与失败会使人谦卑。
Iris excused herself with humble words. 艾丽斯用谦逊的言词为自己辩解。
He fought many hard battles and achieved notable merits， but he remainshumble in spirits. 他参加过许多战役， 立下了汗马功劳， 但他仍然很谦虚。

yingyinNormal.en: Welcome to our humble home. You live here?
yingyinNormal.zh: 欢迎来到寒舍你们住在这里呀？

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, the humble tomato, the foundation of pizza sauce.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是啊，这小小的番茄，就是披萨酱的基础。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah. But don't worry, I will remain the same down-to-earth humble Joe I've always been.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不过别担心，就像现在这样，我将依然是你们接地气的小伙伴。

yingyinNormal.en: Finnick Odair, right? Yes. He won his Games at 14. Youngest ever. Extremely humble. You're kidding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是芬尼克欧戴尔吧？没错，他14岁赢了比赛，是最年轻的冠军，为人很绅士。开玩笑 。

yingyinNormal.en: From our humble beginnings, and throughout the past 15 years, Alibaba has changed commerce in China.
yingyinNormal.zh: 从我们最初很单纯的一个小期望开始，如今十五年过去了，阿里巴巴已经改变了中国电子商务的模式。

yingyinNormal.en: For nearly 60 years, this humble patch of earth on the outskirts of town has been transformed into a frozen fantasy land.
yingyinNormal.zh: 近60年来，哈尔滨郊外这块不起眼的土地变身成为一块冰封的梦幻世界。

yingyinNormal.en: Not so quick, Humble. Yeah. Actually when it's your year it is believed you are going to get more bad luck. Really? Yeah. How come?
yingyinNormal.zh: 别高兴得太早，其实到了本命年，人们认为会更容易倒霉。真的? 对。为什么？

yingyinNormal.en: My small rectory abuts her estate, Rosings Park, and she often condescends to drive by my humble dwelling in her little phaeton and ponies.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的小教区毗邻她的庄园，罗新斯花园。她还常乘她的四轮小马车拜访过我的寒舍。

yingyinNormal.en: Figured your stories could use a little embellishment. You know, I always felt this place was missing a real villain. Hence my humble contribution.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我只是觉得你的故事可以加点修饰，我一直觉得这个地方缺少一名真正的反派角色，所以我尽绵薄之力了。

yingyinNormal.en: It is difficult to imagine more humble origins than those of the genius now cooking at Gusteau's, who is, in this critic's opinion, nothing less than the finest chef in France.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现今在食神餐厅掌厨的天才们出身之低微令人难以想像，依个人的看法，他是法国最优秀的厨师。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, Dave, bikes are an important form of transport in China, planes and trains can be too expensive for people, so the humble bike is often the only way thousands of workers can get home.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对，戴夫，摩托是中国的一种重要运输形式，火车和飞机对于人们来说可能太昂贵了，所以简陋的摩托车就成了成千上万的农民工唯一的回家方式。

yingyinNormal.en: Trust me, call her. Fine. It's a shame you didn't go to dinner with us, because the buffet you're about to enjoy only serves humble pie, a dessert much less tasty than frozen yogurt. I was this close.
yingyinNormal.zh: 听我的，打给她吧。行，你没跟我们一起吃晚餐，真可惜，因为你等下就只能尝到屈辱的滋味了，跟冰酸奶的味道完全不能比哦，当时就坐这么近。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Humble</highlight> people do not ignore, avoid, or try to deny their limits or deficiencies.
